0:The Gero Froggy specialty shop was called “Toadally Froggy.”[%p]
100:Someone, at some point, must have thought it was a funny pun, but all it could elicit from Ban was a tired sigh.[%p]
200:There were twenty Toadally Froggy stores all across the city, and they were supposedly building more.[%p]
300:The one in Harajuku was the first one that had been built, and so it was a mecca for Gero Froggy fans.[%p]
400:That was the one Ban had decided to visit, and he was quickly regretting it.[%p]
500:[name]判[line]Hmm... Hey, Yua. C-Can I go home?[%p]
