800:[name]判[line]I mean, this clearly isn't a place for a guy my age.[%p]
900:It was right on Takeshita Street, and there were countless young people walking outside, having fun and talking to each other. Most of them were completely ignoring the shop.[%p]
1000:The inside was small, and mostly devoid of people.[%p]
1100:There were only about five people there, including Ban and Yua, and all of them but Ban were teenage girls.[%p]
1200:A guy that looked like Ban walking down Takeshita Street with a teenage girl like Yua probably seemed like he was buying sex.[%p]
1300:And now here he was, buying her the mascot character that all the kids loved. What a perfectly stereotypical old pervert he was. Ban felt depressed.[%p]
1400:And...[%p]
1500:[name]判[line]It feels like somebody's watching us.[%p]
