4000:[name]判[line]Yeah, that's right.[%p]
4100:[name]判[line]She really wanted one.[%p]
4200:[name]判[line]And you know, I figured it wouldn't kill me to act like a dad once in a while. Haha.[%p]
4300:Ban gave the clerk a friendly, awkward-looking grin.[%p]
