5000:[name]ショップ店員[line]And like, don't call them “new editions.” We always call them “new frogs.”[%p]
5100:[name]ショップ店員[line]On Friday, Saturday, and Sunday, they go flying off the shelves. Seriously crazy. They go off the shelves like, “Bang! Bang!”[%p]
